path::Path::as_os_str.doc:
Yields the underlying [`OsStr`] slice.

# Examples

```
use std::path::Path;

let os_str = Path::new("foo.txt").as_os_str();
assert_eq!(os_str, std::ffi::OsStr::new("foo.txt"));
```

